* go fmt

- Tabs? Spaces? go fmt
- Format code on save
- Add it to [[https://gist.githubusercontent.com/judwhite/c92e58607e483811a7eb/raw/b18c0d03cb995f7aad68e73616b6098cb19b7886/test.sh][test.sh]]

